&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prezzeeversary Leave – Extra day of annual leave for each year you’re with us.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BirthYay Leave – Celebrate you with a paid day off during your birthday month.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Novated Car Leasing – A tax-smart way to bundle and pay for your car and running costs.&lt;/li&gt;
